      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Board ¶ of the ¶ Grand-ducal Court Domains ¶ Karlsruhe, 21 August  ¶  ¶ 1879 ¶ To his honour...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">79.08.21a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From the Board of Grand-ducal Domains, Baden</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">General-Landesarchiv, Karlsruhe, 56/3312.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found; MS is a file copy with </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">marginal annotation</seg>
                     <seg style="">: […] 21/8 […] […] 21/8 79.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Intendanz </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">der </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">Grossherzoglichen Hof-Domänen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Karlsruhe, am 21ten August <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times; ">18</seg>79</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">No 1747</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">S Hochwohlgeboren</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">dem englischen Regierungs Botaniker</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Herrn Baron Müller in Melbourne</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Durch Allerhöchste Entschliesung vom 16 d M No 5677 erhielten wir von S.K.H. dem Grosherzog den Auftrag, Eure Hochwohlgeborn für die Schenkung der schönen Baumfarren in Höchst[…] Namen den verbindlichsten Dank auszusprechen welchen Auftrags wir uns hiedurch zu erledigen die Ehre haben.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>[…]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Illegible initials</seg>
                     <seg style="">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Board</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">of the</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Grand-ducal Court Domains</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Karlsruhe, 21 August <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>1879</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">To his honour</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">the English Government Botanist</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Müller in Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By highest resolution of the 16th of this month, number 5677, we received from His Royal Highness the Grand Duke the instruction to express in his name the most gracious thanks to your honour for the gift of the beautiful tree ferns,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to C. Mayer, 20 February 1879.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> which instruction we have the honour to discharge by this.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">[…]<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Illegible initials</seg>
                     <seg style="">.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
